title: Shaker Style Wood Cabinets, Gray Quartz Countertops, Tennis Court
posting_body: ['Westside Terrace', '3636 South Sepulveda, Blvd., Los Angeles, CA, 90034', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 28', 'OR Text', '28', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Welcome Home!', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 601 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'There is no other apartment community quite like Westside Terrace Apartments.', 'Here residents play tennis on the three courts, swim in the spectacular pool, exercise in the spacious fitness center and compete on game tables, including billiards, and a table tennis.', 'Our surround-sound media room features theater seating.', 'For those who appreciate deluxe living, choose the option of newly-renovated apartments featuring stainless steel appliances, gray granite countertops, shaker style wood cabinets and vinyl wood-like flooring.', 'Students and busy professionals can make use of the conference room and business center.', 'Your renovated home – and all the excitement of this community - is waiting for you at Westside Terrace.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.', 'Please contact our leasing office for current pricing and specials.', 'Features', '- Newly-Renovated Apartments', '- Gray Quartz Countertops', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Shake Style Wood Cabinets', '- Vinyl Wood-like Flooring', 'Community Amenities', '- Fitness Center', '- Spa', '- Tennis Court', '- Controlled Access Parking', '- Pool', '- Laundry Facility', 'Office Hours', 'Monday - Sunday: 9am to 6pm', 'Photos displayed are a representation of the community but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Availability and rental rates are updated daily, and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please contact the property for current availability and pricing.', 'l2zfcIg0J42r']
